HB 1082 Original 2026 Regular Session Dewitt
Abstract: Provides relative to venue in suits against the Municipal Police Employees'
Retirement System.
Present law (C.C.P. Art. 84) requires actions involving the Municipal Police Employees'
Retirement System to be brought in the parish of East Baton Rouge or in the parish of the
domicile of the retirement system or employee benefit program.
Proposed law amends present law to require actions involving the Municipal Police
Employees' Retirement System to be instituted before the district court of the judicial district
in which the employer is located.
(Amends C.C.P. Art. 84; Adds C.C.P. Art. 84.1)
